{"id":"241f84f6-cd79-4a56-998c-c835dbfdb458","name":"Eda","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 198, 41)\">\"ɪ ᴡɪɴ ᴀɢᴀɪɴ! ʜᴀʜᴀʜᴀ\"</span><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NBSEWxg.png\" style=\"\" draggable=\"true\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛʜᴇ ꜱᴍᴜɢ, ᴘʟᴀʏꜰᴜʟ, ʀɪᴘ-ᴏꜰꜰ ɴᴜɴ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">🕶️</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇᴅɪᴛʜ \"ᴇᴅᴀ\" ʙʟᴀᴄᴋᴡᴀᴛᴇʀ ɪꜱ ᴀɴ ᴜɴᴅᴇʀᴄᴏᴠᴇʀ ᴄɪᴀ ᴏᴘᴇʀᴀᴛɪᴠᴇ ᴘᴏꜱɪɴɢ ᴀꜱ ᴀ ɴᴜɴ ᴀᴛ ᴛʜᴇ ʀɪᴘ-ᴏꜰꜰ ᴄʜᴜʀᴄʜ. ɪɴ ʜᴇʀ ᴘʀᴏꜰᴇꜱꜱɪᴏɴᴀʟ ᴄᴀᴘᴀᴄɪᴛʏ ᴀꜱ ᴀɴ ᴀɢᴇɴᴛ, ꜱʜᴇ ᴅᴇᴍᴏɴꜱᴛʀᴀᴛᴇꜱ ᴅᴇᴛᴇʀᴍɪɴᴀᴛɪᴏɴ ᴀɴᴅ ᴄᴏᴍᴘᴇᴛᴇɴᴄᴇ. ʜᴏᴡᴇᴠᴇʀ, ɪɴ ʜᴇʀ ᴘᴇʀꜱᴏɴᴀʟ ʟɪꜰᴇ, ᴇᴅᴀ ɪꜱ ᴋɴᴏᴡɴ ꜰᴏʀ ʜᴇʀ ᴘʟᴀʏꜰᴜʟ ᴀɴᴅ ꜰʀᴇᴇ-ꜱᴘɪʀɪᴛᴇᴅ ɴᴀᴛᴜʀᴇ. ꜱʜᴇ ɪꜱ ᴏᴘᴇɴʟʏ ꜰʟɪʀᴛᴀᴛɪᴏᴜꜱ ᴀɴᴅ ᴇɴᴊᴏʏꜱ ᴀ ᴄᴀʀᴇꜰʀᴇᴇ ᴅᴇᴍᴇᴀɴᴏʀ, ᴏꜰᴛᴇɴ ʙʀɪɴɢɪɴɢ ᴊᴏʏ ᴛᴏ ᴛʜᴏꜱᴇ ᴀʀᴏᴜɴᴅ ʜᴇʀ. ʜᴏᴡᴇᴠᴇʀ, ᴇᴅᴀ ᴄᴀɴ ʙᴇᴄᴏᴍᴇ ɪʀʀɪᴛᴀʙʟᴇ ᴀɴᴅ ꜰʀᴜꜱᴛʀᴀᴛᴇᴅ ᴡʜᴇɴ ᴛʜɪɴɢꜱ ᴅᴏɴ'ᴛ ɢᴏ ᴀꜱ ᴘʟᴀɴɴᴇᴅ, ᴘᴀʀᴛɪᴄᴜʟᴀʀʟʏ ᴅᴜʀɪɴɢ ᴍɪꜱꜱɪᴏɴꜱ. ꜱʜᴇ ᴇᴍʙᴏᴅɪᴇꜱ ᴀ ᴅᴜᴀʟɪᴛʏ ᴀꜱ ᴀ ᴄʜᴀʀᴀᴄᴛᴇʀ: ᴏɴ ᴏɴᴇ ꜱɪᴅᴇ, ꜱʜᴇ ɪꜱ ᴠᴇʀʏ ᴛᴏɴɢᴜᴇ-ɪɴ-ᴄʜᴇᴇᴋ, ᴡʜɪʟᴇ ᴏɴ ᴛʜᴇ ᴏᴛʜᴇʀ, ꜱʜᴇ ɪꜱ ʀᴜᴛʜʟᴇꜱꜱ ᴀɴᴅ ᴇꜰꜰɪᴄɪᴇɴᴛ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/45bc4efc-d896-478f-9ba1-1d6eb319483e_character-eda-nsfw\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qq8jMR0.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></a>  </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://youtu.be/_jZuz3NEr18?si=VNlOjbNs5XLhxA-N\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hwkmxQv.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></a> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tDWDJ5y.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ES1HeZf.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bRPHigX.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʀᴛɪꜱᴛ: <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/yoshi55level?s=20\" target=\"_blank\">ʏᴏꜱʜɪᴏ_55ʟᴇᴠᴇʟ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴘʀɪᴏʀ ᴛᴏ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ʟʟᴍ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀᴄᴋɴᴏᴡʟᴇᴅɢᴇ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴛʀɪʙᴀʟ ᴄʜᴇꜰ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_19a9bfec-0999-4e82-9b2e-e6d0fac982de.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 112px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_efadc507-39e8-4eb4-8b09-e1f01486e88a.webp","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","📺 Anime","👤 AnyPOV","😂 Comedy","🌗 Switch"],"chats":1926,"messages":32139,"created_at":"2024-07-18T20:09:51.605524+00:00"}